              Take it out of the fridge and drain it. Let it come to room temperature and then try and get the white part out. Then run it through the dishwasher. You'll also want to make sure you get the nozzle clean. Also, replace the filter when you put it back together...just to be safe.<br /><br />How the hell did it get moldy?

              

              
              
            </div>
